refentry.refsect1:
  &reftitle.examples;

   MongoClient::listDBs 例子


    例子演示了如何列出数据库，并返回数据的结构。



<?php

$mongo = new MongoClient();
$dbs = $mongo->listDBs();
print_r($dbs);

?>


   &example.outputs.similar;


Array
(
    [databases] => Array
        (
            [0] => Array
                (
                    [name] => doctrine
                    [sizeOnDisk] => 218103808
                    [empty] =>
                )
        )

    [totalSize] => 218103808
    [ok] => 1
)
